OL,3,CChampion horse trainer found guilty of
OL,4,Clate-night assault on dog walker
OL,6,FA champion horse trainer could be
OL,7,Fjailed after he was convicted of
OL,8,Fassaulting a dog walker who was on his
OL,9,Fland late at night.
OL,11,FRichard Evan Rhys Williams, known as
OL,12,FEvan Williams, repeatedly struck
OL,13,FMartin Dandridge, 72, with a hockey
OL,14,Fstick during a night-time assault.
OL,16,FMr Dandridge, from Swindon, Wiltshire,
OL,17,Fsuffered injuries including a
OL,18,Ffractured arm in the incident on
OL,19,FWilliams' land at Llancarfan, Vale of
OL,20,FGlamorgan, on 4 December, 2024.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/10
