PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1773144737
OL,3,CChampion horse trainer found guilty of
OL,4,Clate-night assault on dog walker
OL,6,F"In that time you will be contacted by
OL,7,Fprobation so they can prepare a
OL,8,Freport, and it is very important you
OL,9,Fco-operate with them."
OL,11,FThe court heard Mr Dandridge was
OL,12,Fstaying at a holiday cottage near to
OL,13,FWilliams' racehorse training centre.
OL,15,FMr Dandridge took his cockerpoo
OL,16,FGulliver for a walk in a paddock that
OL,17,Fwas part of the stables, and because
OL,18,Fit was dark was using a torch.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@VO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/10
