PN,46207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1773144737
OL,3,CChampion horse trainer found guilty of
OL,4,Clate-night assault on dog walker
OL,6,FThere had been incidents of fly-
OL,7,Fgrazing on Williams's property in the
OL,8,Fpast ` where animals are left on land
OL,9,Fwithout permission ` as well as hare
OL,10,Fcoursing and poaching, the court heard.
OL,12,FHis family spotted the lights on their
OL,13,Fland and believed Mr Dandridge was
OL,14,Flamping, when people use bright lights
OL,15,Fto find animals such as rabbits and
OL,16,Ffoxes, often with a dog.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
