FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1773144737
OL,3,CChampion horse trainer found guilty of
OL,4,Clate-night assault on dog walker
OL,6,FWilliams told the court he did not
OL,7,Finjure Mr Dandridge and maintained he
OL,8,Fwas hurt after being pulled over on
OL,9,Fthe rough terrain by his out-of-
OL,10,Fcontrol dog and had fallen into a
OL,11,Fdrainage hole.
OL,13,F"If we hadn't acted in the way we had,
OL,14,FMr Dandridge could have been on his
OL,15,Fown, hit his head, and we could be
OL,16,Flooking at serious, serious, serious
OL,17,Fdeath," the father-of-three said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUyD@GO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/10
