PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1773144737
OL,3,CChampion horse trainer found guilty of
OL,4,Clate-night assault on dog walker
OL,6,FWilliam Bebb, prosecuting, asked the
OL,7,Fdefendant if he was the hero, and he
OL,8,Freplied: "I'm no hero. I'm only saying
OL,9,Fthat Mr Dandridge's unfortunate lack
OL,10,Fof control of his dog caused his
OL,11,Finjury."
OL,13,FMr Bebb suggested Williams's account
OL,14,Fof an out-of-control dog was
OL,15,F"nonsense".
OL,26,@pD@JOUsD@HO]wD@AOUwD@JO]
