PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1773144737
OL,3,CChampion horse trainer found guilty of
OL,4,Clate-night assault on dog walker
OL,6,F"You were filled with rage due to the
OL,7,Fnature of the background you had with
OL,8,Flampers," he said. "Whether a broken
OL,9,Fbone or a wound, you wanted to teach
OL,10,Fthose lampers a lesson. I suggest you
OL,11,Fstruck him repeatedly, swearing and
OL,12,Fshouting as you did."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@IO]pD@TOUtD@UO]
